description:
Objective: Brew all 9 main types of potions as quickly as possible. The 9 types are Regen, Healing, Fire Resistant, Strength, Speed, Slowness, Harming, Weakness, and Poison.
Difficulty: Hardcore
Structures: On
Rules: No F3 and no beds.
